# STATS::PLAYSTATS_PEGASUS_AS_PERSONAL_AIRCRAFT

## Summary
Telemetry sent whenever a player converts certain pegasus vehicles into personal vehicles by driving them into the player owned hanger

## Parameters
* **INT** vehicleId
